data.description: Come see this beautiful home located in Heartland. This home boasts one of the biggest lots in the community. The size of the backyard is a must see! The home has been meticulously maintained and cared for. There are four spacious bedrooms and three full bathrooms. The floor plan is open and bright with abundant natural light!  There is plenty of closet space in the primary bedroom as well as space in the bedroom to accommodate a king size bedroom set. Waking trails, pools, water sides, soccer fields, are just some of the many amenities to enjoy! A perfect place for a family or someone just looking to enjoy a quiet neighborhood!
